      <prop type="x-translation-ref">渭陽.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>我送舅氏，曰至渭陽。何以贈之，路車乘黃。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I escorted my mother's nephew,
To the north of the Wei
What did I present to him ?
Four bay horses for his carriage of state.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
